{"title":"永远的微笑——献给敬爱的邓小平同志","authors":["晓雪"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":3,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给敬爱的邓小平同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却留下一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切的、慈爱的、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的微笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您微笑着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着您亲爱的人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着您伟大的祖国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从列宁到毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在二十世纪离去的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代伟人中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您最后微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却笑得最开心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最舒畅、最好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三山五岳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的微笑中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高昂起头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江小河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的微笑中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路欢歌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳、上海、大连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座座现代化的大厦高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的微笑中迅速崛起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港、澳门、台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的微笑中将陆续"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回到祖国怀抱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三起三落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三落三起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去的伟绩丰功和艰险坎坷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您从来不说。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您总是微笑着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前看——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在您的微笑中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世纪的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即将升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看世界的东方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞光万道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九九七年二月二十一日，昆明"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}